- Added `controls.filevault.prompt_enablement_at` (macOS, Fleet Premium) to defer FileVault enablement to logout so an external login-time enabler can own enablement. `login` (default) keeps Fleet's current force-at-login and Setup Assistant enforcement; `logout` drops those force keys while still escrowing the recovery key and preventing disk encryption from being disabled. `enable_disk_encryption` remains the on/off; Windows BitLocker and Linux LUKS are unaffected.
